window.bookSummaryJSON = "Robin Hobb's thrilling Soldier Son trilogy comes to its conclusion in <i>Renegade's Magic</i>. Nevare Burvelle stands accused of a host of heinous crimes, including murder. And he remains under the thrall of the Speck magic that twists his psyche into a ruthless alter-ego. But all is not lost. Perhaps if he asserts control of this other self, he will emerge transformed and triumphant."; 
